Inside /etc/apache2/mods-enabled/mpm_prefork.conf change to:
  <IfModule mpm_prefork_module>
          StartServers                     5
          MinSpareServers           5
          MaxSpareServers          10
          ServerLimit               1200
          MaxRequestWorkers         1200
          MaxConnectionsPerChild    1000 
</IfModule>

run service apache2 reload
